title: British boxing champ Adams inspires Barbie
text:
British boxing champ Adams inspires Barbie Wednesday, March 07, 2018 - 01:33 
A Barbie doll in the likeness of British Olympic boxing champion Nicola Adams has been unveiled along with 13 other 'Sheroes' to mark International Women’s Day. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
